sys_update_xml.name: sysevent_script_action_d92636b2975301008e00958e3b297567
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sysevent_script_action"><sysevent_script_action action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>false</active><condition_script/><description/><event_name>login.failed</event_name><name>SNC User Lockout Check with Auto Unlock</name><order>100</order><script><![CDATA[//
// Check to see if the user has failed to login too many times
// when the limit is reached, lock the user out of the system.
// Also create a trigger to unlock the user after 'N' minutes.
//

lockoutOnFailedLogin();

function lockoutOnFailedLogin() {
	var maxUnlockAttempts = gs.getProperty("glide.user.max_unlock_attempts", 5);
	var gr = new GlideRecord("sys_user");
	if (gr.get("user_name", event.parm1.toString())) {
		if (gr.failed_attempts > maxUnlockAttempts)
			return;

		gr.failed_attempts += 1;
		if (gr.failed_attempts > maxUnlockAttempts) {
			gr.locked_out = true;
			gr.update();
			gs.log("User " + event.parm1 + " locked out due to too many invalid login attempts");
			triggerUnlock(gr.sys_id);
		} else {
			gr.update();       
		}
	}
}

function triggerUnlock(userSysID) {
	var unlockIn = gs.getProperty("glide.user.unlock_timeout_in_mins", 15);
	var trigger = new GlideRecord("sys_trigger");
	trigger.name = "Unlock the user after "+ unlockIn + " mins";
	trigger.next_action = getTriggerTime(unlockIn);
	trigger.job_id.setDisplayValue('RunScriptJob');
	trigger.script = getTriggerScript(userSysID);
	trigger.document = 'sys_user';
	trigger.document_key = userSysID;
	trigger.state = 0;
	trigger.trigger_type = 0;
	trigger.insert();
}

function getTriggerScript(userSysID) {
	var ret = ""
	+ "var gr = new GlideRecord('sys_user');\n"
	+ "gr.addQuery('sys_id', '" +userSysID+ "');\n"
	+ "gr.addQuery('locked_out', true);\n"
	+ "gr.query();\n"
	+ "if (gr.next()) {\n"
		+ "gr.locked_out = false;\n"
		+ "gr.failed_attempts = 0;\n"
		+ "gr.update();\n"
		+ "gs.log('Auto-unlocking user '+gr.name);\n"
	+ "} else {\n"
		+ "gs.log('Unable to auto-unlock user with sys_id: "+userSysID+"');\n"
	+ "}";
	return ret;
}

function getTriggerTime(minutesToAdd) {
	var checkTime = new GlideDateTime(/*now*/);
	checkTime.addSeconds(minutesToAdd * 60);
	return checkTime;
}
]]></script><synchronous>true</synchronous><sys_class_name>sysevent_script_action</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2013-08-24 00:27:47</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path/><sys_id>d92636b2975301008e00958e3b297567</sys_id><sys_mod_count>28</sys_mod_count><sys_name>SNC User Lockout Check with Auto Unlock</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="High Security Settings" source="com.glide.high_security">bd56738cc927101091f9f06464832746</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sysevent_script_action_d92636b2975301008e00958e3b297567</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>developer.program@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-02-10 13:49:28</sys_updated_on></sysevent_script_action></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>false</action_insert><action_query>true</action_query><action_update>false</action_update><active>false</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>ecc_queue</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition/><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>Pre-G MID Upgrade ECC Blocker</name><order>100</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous /*null when async*/) {
	var query = current.getEncodedQuery();
	if (query.indexOf('agent') != -1) {
		var agent = '';
		var queryArr = query.split('^');
		for (var i = 0; i < queryArr.length; i++)
			if (queryArr[i].indexOf('agent') != -1)
				agent = queryArr[i].split('=')[1];
		
		var mid = MIDServer.getByName(agent);

		if (mid && mid.isPreGeneva())
			current.addQuery('topic', 'IN', ['SystemCommand', 'HeartbeatProbe']);
	}

})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>will.swift</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2016-03-03 23:49:05</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path/><sys_id>2450c0003702120069da03488e41f1d5</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Pre-G MID Upgrade ECC Blocker</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="MID Server" source="com.glideapp.agent">a4a63740c967101091f9f06464832727</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_2450c0003702120069da03488e41f1d5</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>system</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-02-10 13:37:49</sys_updated_on><template/><when>before</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=2450c0003702120069da03488e41f1d5"/></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>true</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>true</action_update><active>true</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>u_my_email_log</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition table="u_my_email_log">u_direction=outbound^EQ<item display_value="Outbound" endquery="false" field="u_direction" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="=" or="false" value="outbound"/><item endquery="true" field="" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="=" or="false" value=""/></filter_condition><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>Email To</name><order>200</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions>u_my_email_log_user</role_conditions><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous /*null when async*/ ) {

    // Add your code here
	
  // current.u_call_to.setValue("demo");
	
   var email = current.u_email;
    var gr = new GlideRecord('customer_contact');
     var qry = 'email=' + email;
    gr.addEncodedQuery(qry);
    gr.query();
    //Assuming that Phone number is unique.
    while (gr.next()) {
        var a = gr.sys_id;	
	}
	current.u_email_to = a;  
	current.update();

})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-07-08 13:13:19</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>a4b753181b5570108acec803604bcb18</sys_id><sys_mod_count>2</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Email To</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_a4b753181b5570108acec803604bcb18</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-12-09 17:14:24</sys_updated_on><template/><when>after</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=a4b753181b5570108acec803604bcb18"/></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="DELETE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>true</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>false</action_update><active>false</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>u_customtable</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition table="u_customtable">u_direction=inbound^EQ<item endquery="true" field="" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="=" or="false" value=""/></filter_condition><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>Process Call Logs</name><order>100</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions>admin,user_admin</role_conditions><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous /*null when async*/ ) {

    // Add your code here
	
  // current.u_call_to.setValue("demo");
   var num = current.u_phone;
    var gr = new GlideRecord('customer_contact');
    var qry = 'phone=' + num + '^ORmobile_phone=' + num;
    gr.addEncodedQuery(qry);
    gr.query();
    //Assuming that Phone number is unique.
    while (gr.next()) {
        var a = gr.sys_id;	
	}
	current.u_call_from = a;  
	current.update();

})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>pranav</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-03-15 06:45:23</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>fa1d69df2f322010b1b955f62799b6e7</sys_id><sys_mod_count>46</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Process Call Logs</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_fa1d69df2f322010b1b955f62799b6e7</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-06-14 09:32:06</sys_updated_on><template>u_call_to=^EQ</template><when>after</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=fa1d69df2f322010b1b955f62799b6e7"/></record_update>

    // Add your code here

  // current.u_call_to.setValue("demo");

	var num = current.u_phone_number;
    var gr = new GlideRecord('customer_contact');
    var qry = 'phone=' + num + '^ORmobile_phone=' + num;
    gr.addEncodedQuery(qry);

	}
	current.u_calling_from = a;
// 	current.u_call_from = a;  
	current.update();

})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-06-09 10:15:03</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>48d7954f1ba030108acec803604bcbbb</sys_id><sys_mod_count>7</sys_mod_count><sys_name>CallFrom</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_48d7954f1ba030108acec803604bcbbb</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-06-14 10:23:15</sys_updated_on><template/><when>before</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=48d7954f1ba030108acec803604bcbbb"/></record_update>

 var num = current.u_phone;
    var gr = new GlideRecord('customer_contact');
    var qry = 'phone=' + num + '^ORmobile_phone=' + num;
    gr.addEncodedQuery(qry);
    gr.query();
    //Assuming that Phone number is unique.

    }
    current.u_call_to = a;
    current.update();
})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-06-09 06:29:20</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>41e1ac871b2030108acec803604bcb84</sys_id><sys_mod_count>3</sys_mod_count><sys_name>CallTo</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_41e1ac871b2030108acec803604bcb84</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-06-14 09:02:28</sys_updated_on><template/><when>after</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=41e1ac871b2030108acec803604bcb84"/></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>true</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>true</action_update><active>true</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>u_my_calling_log</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition table="u_my_calling_log">u_direction=outbound^EQ<item display_value="Outbound" endquery="false" field="u_direction" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="=" or="false" value="outbound"/><item endquery="true" field="" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="=" or="false" value=""/></filter_condition><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>CallTo</name><order>200</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous /*null when async*/ ) {

    // Add your code here
	
  // current.u_call_to.setValue("demo");
   var num = current.u_phone;
    var gr = new GlideRecord('customer_contact');
    var qry = 'phone=' + num + '^ORmobile_phone=' + num;
    gr.addEncodedQuery(qry);
    gr.query();
    //Assuming that Phone number is unique.
    while (gr.next()) {
        var a = gr.sys_id;	
	}
	current.u_call_to = a;  
	current.update();

})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-06-14 11:11:20</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>75d5d7281b7074108acec803604bcb6d</sys_id><sys_mod_count>2</sys_mod_count><sys_name>CallTo</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_75d5d7281b7074108acec803604bcb6d</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-12-09 17:16:34</sys_updated_on><template/><when>after</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=75d5d7281b7074108acec803604bcb6d"/></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="DELETE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>true</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>false</action_update><active>true</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>u_my_chat_log</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition table="u_my_chat_log">u_direction=inbound^EQ<item display_value="Inbound" endquery="false" field="u_direction" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="=" or="false" value="inbound"/><item endquery="true" field="" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="=" or="false" value=""/></filter_condition><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>ChatFrom</name><order>200</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions>u_my_chat_log_user</role_conditions><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous /*null when async*/ ) {

    // Add your code here
	
  // current.u_call_to.setValue("demo");
	
   var email = current.u_email;
    var gr = new GlideRecord('customer_contact');
     var qry = 'email=' + email;
    gr.addEncodedQuery(qry);
    gr.query();
    //Assuming that Phone number is unique.
    while (gr.next()) {
        var a = gr.sys_id;	
	}
	current.u_chat_from = a;  
	current.update();

})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-06-18 05:11:27</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>32c9aafd1bf838108acec803604bcb04</sys_id><sys_mod_count>6</sys_mod_count><sys_name>ChatFrom</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_32c9aafd1bf838108acec803604bcb04</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-07-15 09:16:16</sys_updated_on><template/><when>after</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=32c9aafd1bf838108acec803604bcb04"/></record_update>
